threads: We had a space named #codeReview. Looks like it is not available now.. Is there a way it can be restored ?
If it was a space that was archived then the only way is through the app. There's not way to restore an archived space via the APIs.
Any Back End support available to restore a deleted Space?
Not that I'm aware of not from the APIs. Can try checking with TAC and see if they have some way of doing it.
